node.text:
Happy Tuesday! Came back from grocery shopping 🤭, never thought grocery shopping would make me this happy 😂
. 
Phase 2 will be starting this weekend. Let’s all be responsible , do not take things for granted & always stay safe ! Remember to wear your mask properly and prepare an extra one in your bag! .
.
Are you heading out this weekend?

@brianteo_tc haha that’s what i feel tooo! 😤sigh!! no choice 🤭🤷🏽‍♀️ !! hahahha
Probably not. Guess will be very crowded. Haha

@rachdaretdream 🤫🤫 of course i going somewhere, cannot wait le.

Nice to be able to go out😊How stunning💞
Hope you have a good Wednesday today! 💖
You are perfection! Share with me your tips how you are so perfect💖
